_exptl_crystal_grow.pdbx_details    
;SIAH1 AT 17.6 MG/ML WAS
MIXED WITH A TWO-FOLD EXCESS OF USP19 PEPTIDE ON ICE FOR
30 MIN. BEFORE SETTING UP FOR CRYSTALLIZATION. CRYSTALS
WERE GROWN AT 298K USING THE SITTING DROP METHOD BY
MIXING 0.5 UL PROTEIN:PEPTIDE MIX WITH 0.5 UL WELL SOLUTION
CONSISTING OF 20% PEG6000, 0.1 M BICINE PH 9.0. THE
CRYSTALS WERE CRYOPROTECTED BY FIRST IMMERSION IN WELL
SOLUTION MIXED WITH 15% (FINAL) ETHYLENE GLYCOL, THEN
IMMERSION IN N-PARATONE.
;
_exptl_crystal_grow.pdbx_pH_range   9.0 
